"Hello, Hippolyte.  You have journeyed beyond your realm to speak to me?," Hera asked. "When you can speak to me in your own village.  Are you alright?" <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A> at: 4/16/01 4:34:07 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 296<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(4/16/01 4:40:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Just a visit</span><hr size=1> &lt;center&gt;<br>
